.TH AUXTOP-X 1 "June 2026" "A/UX Workstation" "Local Commands"
.SH NAME
auxtop-x \- launch auxtop in a themed rxvt (fvwm menu entry)
.SH DESCRIPTION
Opens auxtop(1) in a synthwave rxvt with the right TERMINFO and font.
This is what the "auxtop" entry on the fvwm Main menu runs.
.SH SEE ALSO
auxtop(1), rxvt(1)
